model = DistMult(batches_count=2, seed=555, epochs=1, k=10, loss='pairwise',
    loss_params={'margin': 5}, optimizer='adagrad', optimizer_params={'lr':
    0.1})
X = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a'], ['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'z',
    'a'], ['a', 'z', 'd']])
model.fit(X)
X_test1 = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a']])
X_test2 = np.array([['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'z', 'a']])
preds1 = model.predict(X_test1)
preds2 = model.predict(X_test2)
assert not np.array_equal(preds1, preds2)
